    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 1. HERO -->
  <section class="hero-black">
    <div class="container hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <div class="hero-eyebrow">Factory-Trained · Pro Grand · Pro Harmony · Professional Series</div>
        <h1>Thermador Range Repair in Los Angeles — Pro Grand, Pro Harmony &amp; Professional Series</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">Factory-trained on Star Burner ignition, ExtraLow simmer valves, and dual-fuel diagnostics. Same-day service across Beverly Hills, Bel Air, Malibu, Pacific Palisades, and the rest of LA County.</p>

